snippet.title: Bionicle: Tales Of The Tohunga Walkthrough-Part 1: The Island
snippet.description:
Hello and welcome to HexaHunter's Bionicle: Tales Of The Tohunga Walkthrough,in this video we will go through the beginning of the game, awakening on a beach and summoned by Turaga Whenua to Onu Koro. We will also learn the basics and commands ingame.

Don't forget to LCS (Like, Comment and Suscribe)
